 Por otro, sabemos que la derivada covariante es
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{D\left(JV\right)}{dt}\left(t\right)=\left(JV\right)'\left(t\right)-\left\langle \left(JV\right)'\left(t\right),N\left(t\right)\right\rangle N\left(t\right)=
\]

