\begin_inset Formula $W$
\end_inset

 es paralelo a lo largo de 
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha$
\end_inset

, entonces verifica la EDO
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left(*\right)\qquad\begin{cases}
W'+\left\langle W,N'\right\rangle N=0\\
W\left(t_{0}\right)=\overrightarrow{w_{0}}
\end{cases}
\]

\end_inset

